original: Eklund, Frans Gustav Emanuel, läroverksadjunkt, Vetlanda, f. 18/11/05 i Alingsås av Anders Gust. E. o. Anna Persson. G. 38 m. Greta Amanda Matsson. Barn: Per f. 39, Karl 41, Berit 44. — Stud:ex. i Gbg 25, fil. kand. 29, fil. mag. 31, pro vår v. Vasa h. a. I. i Gbg 40. Vik. ämneslär. i Örkelljunga 32-33, timlär. v. Skoghalls komm. mellansk. 34-35, S:t Sigfrids skolhem i Helgö 35, e. o. ämneslär. v. skeppsgossesk. i Karlskrona 36-37, e. adj. i Karlskrona 37-40, e. o. adj. i Kristinehamn 41-43, adj. i matem., fysik o. kemi v. Vetlanda samrealsk. sed. 43.
translated: Eklund, Frans Gustav Emanuel, high school teacher, Vetlanda, b. November 18, 1905 in Alingsås to Anders Gust. E. and Anna Persson. Married in 1938 to Greta Amanda Matsson. Children: Per b. 1939, Karl b. 1941, Berit b. 1944. Graduated from gymnasium in Gothenburg in 1925, Bachelor of Arts in 1929, Master of Arts in 1931, completed teaching credentials at Vasa högre allmänna läroverk in Gothenburg in 1940. Temporary subject teacher in Örkelljunga from 1932-1933, substitute teacher at Skoghalls kommuns mellanskola from 1934-1935, teacher at S:t Sigfrids skolhem in Helgö in 1935, assistant subject teacher at skeppsgosseskolan in Karlskrona from 1936-1937, assistant teacher in Karlskrona from 1937-1940, assistant subject teacher in Kristinehamn from 1941-1943, and teaching mathematics, physics, and chemistry at Vetlanda samrealskola from 1943.
